sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as MCP Client
  participant CLI as ruflo / cli.js
  participant Tools as mcp-tools registry
  participant Swarm as SwarmCoordinator
  participant Agent as Agent
  participant Memory as HybridBackend
  participant DB as SQLite / AgentDB

  Client->>CLI: JSON-RPC tool call
  CLI->>Tools: callMCPTool(name, params)
  Tools->>Swarm: spawn or execute task
  Swarm->>Agent: executeTask(task)
  Agent-->>Swarm: TaskResult
  Swarm->>Memory: store event/result
  Memory->>DB: structured and vector writes
  Swarm-->>Tools: result and metrics
  Tools-->>CLI: MCP tool result
  CLI-->>Client: JSON-RPC response
